modName: Amitiel - Male Wood Elf Save Added Dark Elf
summary: This is my Wood Elf.  I thought he looked pretty cool so I uploaded him.  Added a dark elf on request.
descriptionHtml:
This is my Wood Elf.  I thought he looked pretty cool so I uploaded him. I HAVE ADDED A BEGINNING SAVE FOR BOTH THE WOOD ELF AND DARK ELF.  My wood elf was fairly far along before.  Now the save starts right after you escape execution at the beginning of the game.

 By the way, I am using Xenius\' character enhancement mod with the optional merged elf and dark elf mods from No Blocky Faces.  Props go to him for his awesome work and allowing me to make a pretty cool looking, IMO, Wood Elf.  I have added a dark elf on request.  I don\'t think he looks as good but I did my best with it.  The dark elf faces are naturally shaped differently than wood elves.
author: Knuxson
